00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:30,600
I don't know the game.

284
00:16:31,150 --> 00:16:34,910
But I know
e-sports is a kind of sportsmanship.

285
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:38,240
It's not just about hiding in
the game, flaunting one's ability.

286
00:16:39,320 --> 00:16:43,840
He has just changed a way
to prove his strength to the world.

287
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:46,073
Just like now,

288
00:16:47,080 --> 00:16:49,440
Ai Jia's taste has improved dramatically.

289
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:52,666
And I have also found the direction
of my future career.

290
00:17:00,600 --> 00:17:02,670
