00:17:58,720 --> 00:18:00,946
And this figure
is actually bigger than,

311
00:18:01,030 --> 00:18:03,110
that of many traditional
athletic projects.

312
00:18:03,510 --> 00:18:06,556
We also know that nowadays
more and more universities,

